    <item>
      <title>西班牙极右翼与保守党因移民问题产生分歧终止联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/spain-s-far-right-conservatives-end-alliance-after-clashing-on-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙主要保守党与极右翼团体在多个地区结成的联盟，因在非法未成年移民待遇问题上发生僵局而破裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/spain-s-far-right-conservatives-end-alliance-after-clashing-on-immigration</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 12:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰联盟未能成功使堕胎合法化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/polish-coalition-fails-in-key-effort-to-decriminalize-abortion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克领导的政府未能以微弱优势通过堕胎合法化法案，这一举动暴露了执政联盟内部在这一导致国家两极分化的问题上的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/polish-coalition-fails-in-key-effort-to-decriminalize-abortion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 11:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
