      <title>中国对六家美国防务公司实施对台武器销售制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/china-sanctions-six-us-defense-companies-for-taiwan-arms-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据中国外交部称，中国因参与最近美国对台出售武器而对六家美国防务公司及其高管实施制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/china-sanctions-six-us-defense-companies-for-taiwan-arms-sale</guid>
