    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯将禁止日本在千岛群岛附近采集海藻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/russia-to-halt-japanese-seaweed-harvesting-near-kuril-islands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯表示，将从下周起暂停日本渔民在长达数十年的领土争端地区附近采伐海藻，在此期间灯塔将进行维护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/russia-to-halt-japanese-seaweed-harvesting-near-kuril-islands</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 11:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
